This repository keeps a narrow QwenVoice helper overlay on top of stock
`mlx-audio` rather than repacking the upstream wheel.

The QwenVoice-specific runtime helper is synced from:

- `third_party_patches/mlx-audio/qwenvoice_speed_patch.py`

to:

- `Sources/Resources/backend/mlx_audio_qwen_speed_patch.py`

Use:

- [build_mlx_audio_wheel.sh](/Users/patricedery/Coding_Projects/QwenVoice/scripts/build_mlx_audio_wheel.sh)

to resync the backend helper after updating the overlay.
